    "long_instructions": "#### Check-In\r\n\r\nDan was playing around with sounds and discovered a groove that he liked, but when he walked away from his computer his little sister ran over and pulled apart all the blocks. Can you help him put his song back together?\r\n\r\n> \"I had the **Cowbell beats** and the **Melody Guitar leads** together, and then I had the **Club beat** and **Guitar Moment lead** together\"\r\n\r\nCan you reconstruct his song? Listen to the Example to hear how it's supposed to sound!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/02d7535d5eb1cf02f5b8051457e061bf-image-1749238267021.png)",
